Class Board

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • Board
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable

    public class Board
extends javax.swing.JComponent
    This class is a JComponent which uses the Graphics2D library to draw the Sudoku grid. The grid contains the 9x9 cells like a Sudoku game, and contains a corresponding Game which contains all information about the current Sudoku being played.
